{"id":558230,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/陶岸君：朝中社檄文共赏/","date":"2017-05-05T07:36:29Z","modified":"2017-05-05T07:36:29Z","title":"陶岸君：朝中社檄文共赏","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1419566295/F1CRAffeT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@陶岸君</a>：朝中社昨天发了个批判我朝的檄文，不过中文版是个删节版，我受累上了朝中社网站上看了全文，实在是太劲爆，不得不分享一下。<br />\n原文实在太长，删掉的除了一些无关紧要的（比如科学论证朝鲜核试验对周边地区无害、声明其拥核是为了自卫等等），有三段是最精彩的。第一段是批判我国如何对朝鲜背信弃义，第二段是细数几十年革命时期朝鲜对我国如何无私奉献仁至义尽，第三段是对我国当前形势的无情嘲讽。<br />\n删掉的位置我在图1中文版中分别进行了标注，对应的译文在图2的相应位置，翻译的不好，无法把朝中社美妙绝伦的文采和造词术全面反映出来，凑合欣赏吧。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wvm1r8jj20sj0qd7i5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558231\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wvm1r8jj20sj0qd7i5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"554\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wvm1r8jj20sj0qd7i5.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wvm1r8jj20sj0qd7i5-300x277.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wvm1r8jj20sj0qd7i5-768x710.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558232\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"660\" height=\"895\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr-221x300.jpg 221w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr-768x1042.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/549cdcd7gy1ff9wwdj0wrj21gv1zq4qr-755x1024.jpg 755w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[18808,8843,9553,20895,22751]}